{"tid":2131183,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"閆麗夢博士公開講緊件事","createTime":"2020-07-29T16:15:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-01T08:55:21.000Z","uid":89641,"like":88,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"0039b4b5880043ba1c890dacf83ee03937a43efb","tid":2131183,"uid":89641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T16:15:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/1152252624856410/wp/867730400302744/?av=904595225\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgroups%2F1152252624856410%2Fwp%2F867730400302744%2F%3Fav%3D904595225&d=6fRpkjTAYTcnGOSNIV5vhM%2BxtiM4uRDursPVmWLIdz4%3D&h=fdaac019\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/1152252624856410/wp/867730400302744/?av=904595225</a><br />\n<br />\n1) 2019年11月尾已經開始研究湖北收到既新病毒樣本<br />\n2) 12月閆博士從中國CDC做野既同學及朋友中得到確認, 佢地更早已經知道呢件事,, 閆博士有keep證據<br />\n____2-1) 12月已經知道有人傳人<br />\n____2-2) 12月已經發生過家庭式群組爆發<br />\n3) 12月已經報告WHO呢件事, 閆博士既LAB係直接under WHO同國際疾控中心 的P3病毒認證及研究中心,佢地既報告具備可信性、權威性, 呢個LAB唔係勁到爆都入唔到去做, 佢地Prove左既野基本上就一定係事實<br />\n<br />\n4) 12月既時候閆博士既上司已經send左report比WHO, 閆博士有keep證據<br />\n5) 1月時, 中國外交團訪美交涉中美貿易戰內容, 同時間WHO公開聲明無傳染病事件發生(但明明有report比佢地,, 閆博士有keep證據)<br />\n6) 見到中國同WHO對全世界講大話, 閆博士開始keep起所有證據, 搵機會走佬到美國<br />\n<br />\n7) 以閆博士既專業意見, 呢隻病毒唔關家禽以致野味市場事, 因為呢隻病毒最容易出現既方法, 就係拎到沙士病毒病株, 搵任何實驗室,半年內就可以製造出來,而病株持有者只有閆博士既港大病毒研究所、解放軍實驗室、疾控中心, 其中解放軍個LAB最有可疑"},{"pid":"2cf0cdfdda399c280b02d300b1a25375905b8f05","tid":2131183,"uid":69221,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T16:19:32.000Z","msg":"還郭文貴一個清白<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n下個係咪到香港民族陣線？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2131139\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2131139</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"7120816a361c2e000c736e77082b08babb5310fc","tid":2131183,"uid":231594,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T16:20:54.000Z","msg":"大把彈藥俾美國<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"023f16d9a029277e00794fdc8ac9f40f19824292","tid":2131183,"uid":124983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T16:21:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f067a76d8cc1f9dec7eb468645dcc995bde8be64","tid":2131183,"uid":100898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T16:23:48.000Z","msg":"Push!!!"},{"pid":"524dd8ce13805cb1468c74b6475180537daa05fe","tid":2131183,"uid":323876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T16:24:55.000Z","msg":"直播定咩來，有字GA"},{"pid":"f1b93e5efa5f24a55923c1835102c312b6f673ec","tid":2131183,"uid":53610,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T16:28:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/nathanlawkc/status/1288465820109230088\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fnathanlawkc%2Fstatus%2F1288465820109230088&d=6fRpkjTAYTcnGOSNIV5vhM%2BxtiM4uRDursPVmWLIdz4%3D&h=24ec0dc5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fnathanlawkc%2Fstatus%2F1288465820109230088&h=1c63b70c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/nathanlawkc/status/1288465820109230088</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/lukedepulford/status/1288460598318161921?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Flukedepulford%2Fstatus%2F1288460598318161921%3Fs%3D21&d=6fRpkjTAYTcnGOSNIV5vhM%2BxtiM4uRDursPVmWLIdz4%3D&h=bdb9d5e9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Flukedepulford%2Fstatus%2F1288460598318161921%3Fs%3D21&h=e1bfa4a1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/luke