-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/BeWaterHKG/status/1288459867099815937</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/KongTsungGan/status/1288471086875774976\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FKongTsungGan%2Fstatus%2F1288471086875774976&d=6fRpkjTAYTcnGOSNIV5vhM%2BxtiM4uRDursPVmWLIdz4%3D&h=8cf3ea68\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FKongTsungGan%2Fstatus%2F1288471086875774976&h=a475b1a5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/KongTsungGan/status/1288471086875774976</a><br />\n<br />\n日文<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/suzutaro26/status/1288472559642542085?s=21[/quote]\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsuzutaro26%2Fstatus%2F1288472559642542085%3Fs%3D21%5B%2Fquote%5D&d=6fRpkjTAYTcnGOSNIV5vhM%2BxtiM4uRDursPVmWLIdz4%3D&h=c3b5b9ea\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsuzutaro26%2Fstatus%2F1288472559642542085%3Fs%3D21%5B%2Fquote%5D&h=efa98f75\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/suzutaro26/status/1288472559642542085?s=21[/quote]</a>"},{"pid":"fd4214d2635ca548bd936cdba7b9949b72fcecac","tid":2131183,"uid":89641,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T16:30:31.000Z","msg":"UPDATE:<br />\n<br />\n8) 武漢肺炎學名就係SARS-2, 絕不可能由自然產生, 因為一開始既30個樣本入面都無生物基因, 而支共係2~3月先公開一個病毒樣本係帶有動物基因而且由頭到尾都係得支共有呢個樣本, 呢個樣本係未特登整出來甚至係未有呢個樣本都係疑問<br />\n9) 不會係野味市場惹返來, 因為一開始幾十個感染者只有一個同果個野味市場有出沒記錄, 其他人既生活痕跡同果度有好遠距離, 而中共卻一直在pin件事去果個野味市場同野生動物身上, 疑似是引導人不去聯想是人為整造既可能性。"},{"pid":"55b1ff0178037fafc0c58c6e24727b548f08d9e3","tid":2131183,"uid":284432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T16:31:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"41e8a657b73d657d982fd8d67d79257a981752bd","tid":2131183,"uid":89641,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"524dd8ce13805cb1468c74b6475180537daa05fe","tid":2131183,"uid":323876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1